content: I was honoured to be one of the guest speakers at Amazon FASTforward, its third sustainability summit for the European transportation industry. At Ecotrans, we're firm believers in zero-emissions, and electric vehicles are our response to this challenge. We took the bold step of purchasing our first fully-electric heavy-duty vehicle. Of course, innovation comes with its set of challenges, and we're ready to tackle them head-on.  We announced as well that we joined The Climate Pledge and we had an interesting conversation with Ruben van Doorn to start soon our partnership with Smart Freight Centre. This summit convened in mid-October in Berlin with industry leaders, fleet operators, manufacturers, researchers, and policy experts from Europe was valuable. Furthermore, ideal place to make new contacts and find more business opportunities. Last not but least, weâ€™ve been part of the Sustainable Fleet Awards and took home the 2023 Mile Master award. It goes to the European carrier who covered the most distance for Amazon using low-carbon fuels (LNG and etrucks). Congrats to our whole team; each award boosts our confidence in going net-zero emissions.  The sky is the limit, come on! ğŸ’ª ğŸšš #eMobility #Transportation #Sustainability #sustainabletransport #SustainableLogistics #Innovation #logistics

content: Dealmate was born with the joined forces of IÃ±igo, Adrian, and Sharon with a common objective. To connect startup founders with talented creatives.Having had experiences on both sides of the table we realize the huge hustle for founders to find reliable and talented creatives to build their vision. After a few bad experiences with Fiverr and other freelancer platforms, they often rely on word of mouth to find studios, agencies, and professionals who can take care of the task without adding extra headaches.On the other hand, talented creatives and professionals seem to have to sell themselves to unfair competition on price in crowded marketplaces or become a social media content machine to stand through the noise, at the cost of not being able to focus on doing the work.This is why Dealmate was born.A curated digital media platform and connector dedicated to communicating the impact of innovation and design, sharing, and amplifying stories from founders and creatives. Dealmate aims to empower the ecosystem by connecting the ambition of startup founders with talented creatives who can make their vision a reality with their skills and expertise.On Dealmate, startup founders will be able to learn, stay up to date, and discover new providers of the services they most need like product design studio, branding, development, legal, paid media, and much more.Then, Dealmate connects founders with a curated network of studios, agencies, and professionals that will excel at their demands, creating a win-win situation where these professionals get offered deals on our platform, without having to be out there selling themselves on social media.To sum up,â€œDealmates is like if Tinder, Uber, and Techcrunch had a babyâ€Are you joining our adventure?
